@startuml
title Concurrent Worker Locking with SKIP LOCKED

participant "Worker A" as WA
participant "Worker B" as WB
participant "execution_queue" as Q
participant "transactions" as T

WA -> Q : SELECT ... FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED LIMIT 1
Q --> WA : row X locked

WB -> Q : SELECT ... FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED LIMIT 1
Q --> WB : row Y or none

WA -> T : load transaction X
WA -> T : update state with optimistic version
WA -> Q : delete/requeue row X

WB -> T : load transaction Y (if any)
WB -> T : update state with optimistic version
WB -> Q : delete/requeue row Y

@enduml
